Sentencas: Ba0.5Sr0.5Co0.8Fe0.2O3-delta(BSCF) powder was prepared via Sol-Gel method.
Titulo: Performance of the Composite Cathode Ba0.5Sr0.5Co0.8Fe0.2O3-δ-Ce0.9Gd0.1O2-δ for Medium-low Temperature Solid Oxide Fuel Cell

Sentencas: Porous BSCF xGDC(x= 30wt%, 40wt%, 50wt%) composite cathodes were prepared via wrapping BSCF powders with Ce0.9Gd0.1O2-delta(GDC) sol.
Titulo: Performance of the Composite Cathode Ba0.5Sr0.5Co0.8Fe0.2O3-δ-Ce0.9Gd0.1O2-δ for Medium-low Temperature Solid Oxide Fuel Cell

Sentencas: The phase composition of the composite cathodes, the morphology of the cross section of the cell, as well as the BSCF particles coated with GDC were characterized with X-ray diffraction, field emission scanning electron microscopy, and transmission electron microscopy, respectively.
Titulo: Performance of the Composite Cathode Ba0.5Sr0.5Co0.8Fe0.2O3-δ-Ce0.9Gd0.1O2-δ for Medium-low Temperature Solid Oxide Fuel Cell

Sentencas: The electrochemical performances of the composite cathodes were studied by impedance spectroscopy.
Titulo: Performance of the Composite Cathode Ba0.5Sr0.5Co0.8Fe0.2O3-δ-Ce0.9Gd0.1O2-δ for Medium-low Temperature Solid Oxide Fuel Cell

Sentencas: The effects of the amount of GDC on the electrochemical performance of the composite cathode were studied by impedance spectroscopy.
Titulo: Performance of the Composite Cathode Ba0.5Sr0.5Co0.8Fe0.2O3-δ-Ce0.9Gd0.1O2-δ for Medium-low Temperature Solid Oxide Fuel Cell

Sentencas: All results showed that the electrochemical performance of the composite cathode greatly improved.
Titulo: Performance of the Composite Cathode Ba0.5Sr0.5Co0.8Fe0.2O3-δ-Ce0.9Gd0.1O2-δ for Medium-low Temperature Solid Oxide Fuel Cell

Sentencas: Electrode polarization resistance of the BSCF-40GDC was the minimum, with the value of 0.397 Omega.cm(2) at 650 degrees C.
Titulo: Performance of the Composite Cathode Ba0.5Sr0.5Co0.8Fe0.2O3-δ-Ce0.9Gd0.1O2-δ for Medium-low Temperature Solid Oxide Fuel Cell

Sentencas: The maximum power density of the single cell was 0.514 W/cm(2) with the values of Ohmic resistance at 0.257 Omega.cm(2) and the polarization resistance at 0.0588 Omega.cm(2), by using H-2 +3%H2O as fuel and air as oxidizing gas at 650 degrees C.
Titulo: Performance of the Composite Cathode Ba0.5Sr0.5Co0.8Fe0.2O3-δ-Ce0.9Gd0.1O2-δ for Medium-low Temperature Solid Oxide Fuel Cell
